      "description": "Validation of CFD-predicted hemolysis index against in-vitro measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump across five adult operating points. All RH predictions within ±12% of measured values. Dataset collected and analysis completed Q3 2021 prior to paediatric and high-flow envelope expansion."
