      "rationale": "In-vitro test loop operated at 37 °C with bovine blood at physiological hematocrit (40 ± 2%). Flow rates controlled to ±0.05 L/min, rotational speed to ±10 RPM. Boundary condition correspondence documented in 2021 validation report. Paediatric and high-flow conditions were not part of the test matrix."
