      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis power-law model are justified by literature and sensitivity analysis at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmarks for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen–Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model applied. Sensitivity analysis confirmed RH predictions are not strongly sensitive to turbulence model choice within the adult operating range. No model-form sensitivity study has been conducted for paediatric Reynolds number regimes."
    },
    {
