      "rationale": "Blood viscosity modelled as Newtonian (μ = 0.0035 Pa·s) consistent with high-shear CPB conditions. Inlet velocity profiles derived from upstream piping geometry. Rotational speed specified as nominal with ±10 RPM uncertainty. Input characterisation adequate for the adult operating range validated in 2021."
    },
